        <div class="small-6 columns">
            <h4>Game Name 1</h4>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Quasi iusto reprehenderit voluptatem odio deleniti provident aliquam qui magnam aspernatur necessitatibus.</p>
